    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/828b69218a68f21831333534c341434f.apng?t=1761238818\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/828b69218a68f21831333534c341434f.poster.avif?t=1761238818\" class=\"bb_img\" width=483 height=63 /></picture></span><br><br>Grooveyard is a chill puzzle game brimming with humor and skeletons. Use your magical powers to manipulate walls and guide your skeletal minions to freedom. Enjoy a mix of strategy and rhythm as you uncover the secrets of your bodiless origins.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.poster.avif?t=1761238818\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.webm?t=1761238818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/5728bb3a50ccc55589b1733379d9ac1b.mp4?t=1761238818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grooveyard features six unique worlds, each with its own aesthetic and challenges. Start in a traditional graveyard, master wall-jumping in a ruined cathedral, unlock doors in an underground prison, navigate broken tiles in a crystallized cave, and defy gravity in a hellish palace. Finally, test your skills in the ultimate world. Each puzzle offers multiple solutions, rewarding clever and efficient play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/660fb0098c87fa5433e1ef74c513e8ca.apng?t=1761238818\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/660fb0098c87fa5433e1ef74c513e8ca.poster.avif?t=1761238818\" class=\"bb_img\" width=483 height=105 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/596aa73080df4f942b5b59ca4f860ec3.webp?t=1761238818\" width=18 height=22 /></span>  Over 60 puzzles across six unique worlds with distinct themes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/15f682a0287ad54145344b9ce075041a.webp?t=1761238818\" width=20 height=18 /></span>  Speak with all your freed skeletons to unravel the mystery of the Grooveyard.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/cbe3156b1310baa224c0a1eba4786305.webp?t=1761238818\" width=20 height=30 /></span>  Optimize your solutions to receive higher ratings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/4d6decf00d189b3a4c4047a23e5aa58c.webp?t=1761238818\" width=22 height=22 /></span>  Gameplay syncs with the music to create unique lofi-beats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/5ab2ba2392a603f64085823156134f10.webp?t=1761238818\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  Fun and relaxed, perfect for a spooky challenge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/7acf79c45fd7c5c3d2a87034f99033ac.apng?t=1761238818\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107360/extras/7acf79c45fd7c5c3d2a87034f99033ac.poster.avif?t=1761238818\" class=\"bb_img\" width=422 height=124 /></picture></span>",
